{"word":"G4339 - προσήλυτος - prosḗlytos - pros-ay'-loo-tos - Proselyte","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσήλυτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosḗlytos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-ay'-loo-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Proselyte</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வேறுமார்க்கத்தான், வேறு மார்க்கத்தமைந்தவன் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. a newcomer a stranger, alien"},{"paragraph":"2. a proselyte"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the alternate of <a href=\"#/G4334 - προσέρχομαι - prosérchomai - pros-er'-khom-ahee/4334\">G4334</a>; an <i>arriver</i> from a foreign region, that is, (specifically) an <i>acceder</i> (<i>convert</i>) to Judaism (&ldquo;proselyte&rdquo;): - proselyte.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}